item.title: End NM-76 North at NM-75
item.description: End NM-76 north at NM-75. Turn right on NM-76 north to continue on the High Road To Taos Scenic Byway.

item.title: NM-76 North - Entering Chamisal
item.description: Entering Chamisal on NM-76 north. Speed Limit 40 MPH through Chamisal.

item.title: NM-76 North - Entering Las Trampas
item.description: Entering Las Trampas on NM-76 north.

item.title: NM-76 North - Taos County
item.description: Entering Taos County on NM-76 north. County line signs in New Mexico tend to have the words "County Line" in all capital letters in a smaller font below the county name.

item.title: End NM-503 East at NM-76
item.description: End NM-503 east at NM-76. Turn right on NM-76 for Truchas. Turn left on NM-76 for Chimayo.

item.title: End NM-503 East at NM-76
item.description: End NM-503 East at NM-76 in rural Rio Arriba County. NM-76 is the High Road To Taos Scenic Byway.
